:: Title
<div class="title-shell">
  <p class="title-kicker">A short mystery</p>
  <h1 class="title-name">Mansion of Ashes</h1>
  <p class="title-meta">20–25 minutes <span class="inline-sep">·</span> three endings <span class="inline-sep">·</span> SugarCube 2</p>
</div>

<hr class="scene-break">

<div class="title-intro">
The house waits above a long slope of wet grass, its windows black, its upper masonry still stained from a fire that ended twelve years ago.

You do not remember how you came here. You remember smoke. You remember a locked door. You remember waking in a bed that is not yours.
</div>

<hr class="scene-break">

<div class="title-actions">
  [[Begin->Bedroom]]
  [[Preferences->Preferences]]
  [[Audio credits->Credits: Audio]]
  <<if !$audioEnabled>>
  <<link "Enable audio">><<set $audioEnabled = true>><<goto "Title">><</link>>
  <<else>>
  <<link "Mute audio">><<set $audioEnabled = false>><<audio ":all" stop>><<goto "Title">><</link>>
  <</if>>
</div>

